description:
This is a 10 minute workout called '10 MIN PERFECT ABS WORKOUT (NO EQUIPMENT BODYWEIGHT WORKOUT!)' from the channel Fraser Wilson.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.
